{"tid":2215240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梅窩英國大叔｜棄銀行筍工為李小龍移民香港 最愛食乳鴿行深水埗 「香港人好誠實 唔會見西人就呃」","createTime":"2020-09-24T00:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T14:27:05.000Z","uid":271829,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"5878d4ca815b67f9015c29aa633f41e2883dbd32","tid":2215240,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T00:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Vs5Kl9AoeLgts1TAy4iKLkvsFE8=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/S6X2EYV64ZF75BLTP4CCCFVTKA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVs5Kl9AoeLgts1TAy4iKLkvsFE8%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FS6X2EYV64ZF75BLTP4CCCFVTKA.jpg&h=01383fdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n深水埗黃金商場四通八達，攝影師常去也認不到路，Gary卻一馬當先，為我們找出路。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n自1980年代首次來香港旅行，愛上香港的英國人Gary Brightman告訴我，愛一個地方，愛一個人，不用宣之於口。也許這是英倫人的含蓄，任你怎樣問，他也不在鏡頭前說：「I love Hong Kong ！」太俗氣了，但他會鬼馬地告訴你his way of loving&mdash;&mdash;帶我到黃金電腦商場尋寶，拐幾個彎，正宗港人攝影師認不到出路，他卻馬上指出出口，帶領我們出去。他招積笑道：「都話我係香港人！」<br />\n他愛吃乳鴿，愛飲茶，最愛是儲超級市場印花。黑色背包寫上自己名字Gary，像小學生。他笑說，因為這是超市用印花換來的背包，人人都有，他怕認錯，才寫上名字。「Am I so Hong Kong ?」他摸摸自己的大肚子，哈哈大笑。<br />\n這個廣東話只會說「唔該哂」，連「香港」也讀得歪歪曲曲的「鬼佬」，又算不算「好鍾意」香港呢？<br />\n<br />\n1986年首次來港 難忘啟德低飛民居<br />\n2009年移民至香港的Gary，59歲，早已拿到香港永久居民的身份，而一切關於香港的印象，始於1986年夏天的假期。當年，他和幾個朋友來港旅行。他聽說啟德機場的降落非常刺激，會穿越越民居，所以在黃昏五六點飛機準備降落，低飛盤旋時，他看出窗口，果然飛機在幾棟民居中間飛過，他看到有人在廚房洗菜、有人在洗衣服。「Oh that&rsquo;s Asia！」他覺得神奇又刺激，走出機場大堂，他看到幾個遊客穿着「I survived」的T-shirt，「這些細節仍然記憶猶新！」他說道。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200924/CW5PTWP2UBAMFDI5V5JFJUCACI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200924%2FCW5PTWP2UBAMFDI5V5JFJUCACI%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFD632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=2227f09c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200924%2FCW5PTWP2UBAMFDI5V5JFJUCACI%2F&h=4f23fc15\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200924/CW5PTWP2UBAMFDI5V5JFJUCACI/</a>"},{"pid":"46d4b19c0c5357b8fa898476bd043de03b7f503c","tid":2215240,"uid":133033,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:39:55.000Z","msg":"點解佢咁鐘意香港 但唔會學廣東話 淨講都好呀<br />\n但你又唔可以話佢唔係香港人"},{"pid":"b79d748d1241fe69f8ebb0a634acf3a41d6b6b76","tid":2215240,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46d4b19c0c5357b8fa898476bd043de03b7f503c","tid":2215240,"uid":133033,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:39:55.000Z","msg":"點解佢咁鐘意香港 但唔會學廣東話 淨講都好呀<br />\n但你又唔可以話佢唔係香港人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:46:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2813baccc7af33f23590ef9249ac8051502b9b7e","tid":2215240,"uid":8014,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:49:13.000Z","msg":"咁鐘意香港 <br />\n<br />\n買左好撚鐘意香港月餅食未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b544ebec6e303ab2bc0f726f3acdf315bf6be0","tid":2215240,"uid":301989,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"2813baccc7af33f23590ef9249ac8051502b9b7e","tid":2215240,"uid":8014,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:49:13.000Z","msg":"咁鐘意香港 <br />\n<br />\n買左好撚鐘意香港月餅食未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:50:03.000Z","msg":"關你撚事呀五毛"},{"pid":"6da93d1cb6cfc96bfebfb5d68e1ed9fbbc9f53b5","tid":2215